Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.57,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗之中 震撼心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:21.74,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,那觉醒的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:24.78,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,立于大地的那身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.95,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,是否为正义的证明？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:32.04,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,传说巨神的那力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:35.00,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直把银河切裂！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:38.25,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,他战斗时的那吼声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:41.09,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,招来闪电雷霆！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:44.13,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要颤抖啊 紧紧盯着哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:49.51,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,那复活的时刻！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:56.27,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,人们还有生灵们 看着这开始的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:01:02.19,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙的逃亡者伊迪安 伊迪安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:09.20,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙的逃亡者伊迪安 伊迪安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.97,0:01:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩他们抛弃了自己的力量无法控制的索罗船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 地球联合军的斯卡拉贝利和巴夫·克兰的伽尔巴巴队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住那个时机 试图夺取索罗船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩他们只好回到索罗船 停止了自爆装置参加了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他们仍来不及解除数枚炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但索罗船的力量将爆炸封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:14.72,T,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194.944,166.686)}憎恨的殖民星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22}翻译：Ross.H 校对：Ross.H&H魂  时轴：H魂 后期：Ross.H 繁化：kinson
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,托拉姆消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,托拉姆消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这里已经忙不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,左舷在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一会就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,增援很快就到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吉拉尔！吉拉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还有十三架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 8点的方向 前面！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,冈加·鲁布队出发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,冈加·鲁布队！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有两台重机动机甲来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,后面有重机动机甲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 还没击落它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,伽达尔·罗队 放出爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要停住巨神机体的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 别管它 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人的本队接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,比现在的战力还要多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莎 吉杰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,三机着舰！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,进行短DS航行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,坐标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,亚空间等级上就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,总之甩掉敌人即可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,DS航行空域 电脑随机选择
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,能量上升 随时可DS航行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,亚空间飞行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的洛古·丹外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想逃到哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,敌舰使用了亚空间飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要立即追击吗 多隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,先进行回收作业再追
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,第一攻击队等下再回收的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没这种必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这个宙域里有个曾被我军攻击的外星人殖民星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,吉杰 记起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是你用准光速导弹攻击的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为了把我们引出来的那个行星...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样道歉也于事无补了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,贝斯 要着陆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,阿基安军已经全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但跟凯拉尔一样 他们应该有剩下的武器弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,到底有多少人幸存呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莎...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是要保护纯粹的血统 作为地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也不坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这也没办法啊 哪里都会蹦出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好攻击的威力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没有造成损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,贝斯 真的要着陆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量寻求阿基安的理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,阿基安 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是索罗星的难民船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,寻求救助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,故意这么说的吧...难民船什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 吃惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点也不吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是经验啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,路 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时候...乖啊 路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,琳 让大家到船中央去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克 阿休拉 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,进入临战态势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的话就强行着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿基安没有回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不太听得清楚...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有了 现在接进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是阿基安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是索罗星的难民船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的是警告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不许再阿基安着陆！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有必要在阿基安着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有必要接纳你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是恶魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,知道现在阿基安还剩多少人口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只有十万啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都是你们来阿基安以后的结果！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快点滚出去...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,索罗船的着陆已经批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请到「通金」点着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们内部有分歧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哈达利 知道「通金」在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 再过二十分钟就可以到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,凭一开始的攻击 我们的民兵就可以简单取胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有背叛和你的约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,扣押他们本来就是你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,按照预定做的话 你们星球剩下的人都能保全了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是这样 古鲁达布拉·多隆阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不能容许索罗船的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是想用自己的力量打倒它...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那交给我们就行 我们双方的利害是一致的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,能相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,交给你行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,武士是不会说谎的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我有多巴总司令的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我多隆的契约书 打完给多巴过目就行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们对您最高的礼节了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,让索罗船进船坞就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那样 到那里由我们解决它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有兴趣给我提建议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你们若给我们本舰甲板的修理的所需
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我就让本舰的非战斗人员离开 到这阿基安上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,贝斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那最好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对阿基安来说 一个女性抵得上数万发导弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我算非战斗员？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们战斗不断扩大 你也注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有无端让自己的生命陷入危险的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但没有我的话 第六文明人和伊迪安的研究就无法...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,伊迪已经发动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,吉杰 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想留在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你还这么想的话 我就到阿基安和你一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不一定是去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,作战顺利开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我军就能不付出任何损伤\N把洛古·丹外星人的船和巨神拿到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,导弹不是装在那边的 转到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,OK OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们去B点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,调整如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,设备还是有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,并且 阿基安的人也在帮忙...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经适应这种情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉拉他们要走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有点舍不得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,会好起来的 贝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,阿休拉 别吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是大人 是非战斗员！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,琳 不要走开为好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,打不开啊 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,打不开？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢莉鲁...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉地说一句 你们已经是人质了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,人质？ 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了结束阿基安上的战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在干嘛呢 休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,船坞的人在休息 就暂时停工了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,吃饭去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 不继续作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,贝斯 船坞的作业员没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哈达利 回舰桥来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,乔立巴 做好起飞准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快启动常规引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人都离开船坞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,离开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那边交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,索罗船开始动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们发觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,联系科莫多亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他背叛了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,乔立巴 引擎达倒临界状态！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 出发后马上合体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莎 出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,吉杰不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他在装导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,遥控伊迪安诺瓦合体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,信号没有出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,能量还未安定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙 把我们的计划告诉索罗船了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你扣了人质吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你那边先不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有人质啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里 看到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是巴夫·克兰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,贝斯 科莫多亚来的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快把索罗船和伊迪安交给巴夫·克兰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不然攻击就无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我可有保护阿基安十万人民的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,科莫多亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,把索罗船和伊迪安交给巴夫·克兰的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了索罗船的女人和孩子已经成人质了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不停止战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把人质一个接一个地宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没吓唬你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,科莫多亚...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢莉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,琳她！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,琳她？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,琳..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,琳 振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不要死啊 琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,琳！琳...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,伊迪安的标志出现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莎 合体吧 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 快速合体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不要出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,回索罗船来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为...为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快躲到索罗船的防护罩里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们后退了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是打倒它的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,停下...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,举起手来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,琳...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,琳...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,6号门有什么动静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,得快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助攻击索罗船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,别做多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,负责人在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是战斗中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不让巴夫·克兰中止攻击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就不能谈判了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们会把索罗船和伊迪安交给巴夫·克兰啰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不要抵抗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,琳她...已经被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 做些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有人质
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在无法救出的情况下...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们把防护罩关掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只凭预感的话 他们不见得会投降的 科莫多亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一会就好 再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还不关掉防护罩 索罗船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等下人质死的可不止一个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,下次是十个！十个！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,吉杰 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,吉杰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让你再杀下去了 科莫多亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道把索罗船交给巴夫·克兰的后果有多么可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,把阿基安卷入战火的你们这帮人还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要用自己的力量保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,都给我杀了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你这混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哈达利 解救出人质了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 我们准备反击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 务必得胜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,为...为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们...卷进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也是被卷进去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,求...求你...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,吉杰！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢莉鲁...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,琳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,琳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,琳...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,琳死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人质的确被解救了 但详细的事我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,琳死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的巴夫·克兰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 伊迪安的仪表...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,巨神过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,全舰脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,科莫多亚死了 只好变更作战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别想逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 波导炮射出了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,波导炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,以最大加速撤离！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,琳...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这么温柔的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么死了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,琳...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,索罗船残酷的命运 才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,多巴全军的包围网正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:26.45,script,,0,0,0,,注释：注意屏幕左下角有一台与基格·马克一样大的\N初代高达/敢达/钢弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我军的包围网 直径大约一百五十光年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,洛古·丹的外星人想不接触任何舰队就逃走是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是知道敌人的动向没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人在古拉巴星域与古鲁达布拉·多隆接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,叫各舰队不要擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要做到彻底的围歼恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,去贯彻到各舰队司令处！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不能独断转行 巨神的力量在我们预料之上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,武士只在乎自己的功绩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,作为奥美财团的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得有必要动用冈多·洛瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,为了军队的面子啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,巴夫·克兰的包围网 让索罗船没有片刻休息的闲暇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,伊迪安诺瓦的驾驶舱被打穿 吉杰在眼前牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,宛如伊迪的发源一般 伊迪安的闪光将星球割做两半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,伊迪发动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 传说巨神伊迪安 宇宙的逃亡者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.87,0:23:34.75,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,被唯一一颗 属于我的星球所抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:42.10,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,誓要能跟你一起 踏上无尽旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:47.64,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,无意间分享 我们的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:55.02,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,同甘共苦 寻欢作乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:24:01.11,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,飞越无限宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:07.70,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你送上真挚的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.04,0:24:13.67,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过无尽银河
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:21.05,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你带去真心的祝福
